# CODEOWNERS — governance repository
#
# The platform team owns everything by default.
# Each team owns their governance subdirectory and can merge changes
# to it without platform team approval.
#
# Replace @your-org/platform-team and team handles with your actual GitHub teams.

# Default: platform team reviews everything
*                              @your-org/platform-team

# Global constitution and governance.yml — broad consensus required
constitution.md                @your-org/platform-team
governance.yml                 @your-org/platform-team
GOVERNANCE-PROCESS.md          @your-org/platform-team

# Domain ownership — update when adding a new domain
constitutions/kafka.md         @your-org/kafka-team
constitutions/camel.md         @your-org/camel-team
adrs/kafka/                    @your-org/kafka-team
adrs/camel/                    @your-org/camel-team
features/kafka/                @your-org/kafka-team
features/camel/                @your-org/camel-team

# Team governance — each team owns their subdirectory
# Add one line per team:
teams/example-team/            @your-org/example-team
# teams/team-payments/         @your-org/team-payments
# teams/team-pos/              @your-org/team-pos
